FBIS4-12696 "drnes070_l_94015" FBIS-NES-94-070 Daily Report 11 Apr 1994 ISRAEL Committee Approves Budget To Pay Hebron Victims Committee Approves Budget To Pay Hebron Victims TA1104101394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0900 GMT 11 Apr 94 TA1104101394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] The Knesset Finance Committee this morning approved a special budget of 19 million shekels to pay compensation to the victims of the Cave of the Patriarchs massacre and their relatives. Our correspondent Hayim Hecht reports that 5 million shekels were allocated to pay for the expenses of the state commission of inquiry and to pay some of the expenses of the hospitals that treated the victims. The sums were approved unanimously.
